overview: The user initiated a request to significantly improve the aesthetic
  appeal of their sleep questionnaire application, which they perceived as
  functional but visually uninspired. The assistant undertook a thorough review
  of the app's existing design, including its global CSS, layout, main pages,
  and various UI components like cards, buttons, progress bars, and form fields.
  This analysis revealed a generic color palette, plain backgrounds, and a lack
  of visual personality suitable for a sleep health app. The assistant then
  implemented a new design strategy, introducing a calming, sleep-themed color
  palette with deep indigo/purple tones and soft teal accents. Key components
  like the QuestionnaireForm, progress bar, IntroSection, CheckboxField, and
  Slider were updated with refined styling, improved layouts, and subtle visual
  enhancements to create a more professional, inviting, and emotionally resonant
  user experience.
